	<!-- 追焰 -->
	<AbilityDef ParentName="RI_PsycastBase">
		<defName>RI_Ability_Fire_Jump</defName>
		<label>Flame teleport</label>
		<description>&lt;color=#FF5832&gt;This technique is learned by the Primordial-spirit maturity rank of the Fire-element Path\n\n&lt;/color&gt;Qi cost: 50\n\nConsume one layer of Life Fire to teleport flames within the selected range.\n\nFlame teleport is said to be the only technique mastered by the founder of Fire method, and it is a top-tier teleportation art.\n\nThe cultivation of this technique is incredibly tedious, requiring the practitioner to focus on the flames for long periods, entering a state of self-forgetfulness. It also requires learning how to ignite one’s own life force, merging fire and life as one.\n\nOnce mastered, the practitioner can transform their physical body completely into a ball of fire, seamlessly traversing between flames within their line of sight, with extraordinary agility.</description>
		<iconPath>UI/Abilities/FireElement/RI_Ability_Fire_Jump</iconPath>
		<cooldownTicksRange>50</cooldownTicksRange>
		<!-- <category>TODO</category> -->
		<displayOrder>200</displayOrder>
		<aiCanUse>true</aiCanUse>
		<verbProperties>
			<verbClass>Verb_CastAbility</verbClass>
			<range>38.9</range>
			<warmupTime>0.5</warmupTime>
			<soundCast>RI_Sound_FireBall_C</soundCast>
			<targetParams>
				<canTargetPawns>false</canTargetPawns>
				<canTargetItems>true</canTargetItems>
				<canTargetLocations>true</canTargetLocations>
			</targetParams>
		</verbProperties>
		<comps>
			<li Class="WhoXiuXian.Abilities.CompProperties__ReduceEnergy">
				<rEnergy>-50</rEnergy>
			</li>
			<li Class="RI_FiveElements.CompProperties_HediffAsEnergy">
				<hediffDef>RI_He_Fire_BurningSoul</hediffDef>
				<useEnergy>1</useEnergy>
				<disableReason>Need one Life fire</disableReason>
			</li>
			<li Class="RI_FiveElements.CompProperties_FireJump"></li>
		</comps>
	</AbilityDef>

	<!-- 乾阳焱火决 -->
	<AbilityDef ParentName="RI_PsycastBase">
		<defName>RI_Ability_Fire_Ring</defName>
		<label>Qianyang flame field</label>
		<description>&lt;color=#FF5832&gt;This technique is learned by the Primordial-spirit combine rank of the Fire-element Path\n\n&lt;/color&gt;Qi cost: 350\n\nConsume one layer of Life Fire to create a domain centered on oneself, where any living being within the domain will be burned by Life Fire.\n\nQianyang Blazing Fire, the ultimate goal of all Fire cultivators. Mastering this technique allows one to ignite their own Life Fire and create a domain of Life Fire.\n\nWithin this domain, all living beings except the practitioner will have their Life Fire ignited, causing them to suffer from the flames burning them from the inside out.</description>
		<iconPath>UI/Abilities/FireElement/RI_Ability_Fire_Ring</iconPath>
		<!--冷却-->
		<cooldownTicksRange>3000</cooldownTicksRange>
		<sendMessageOnCooldownComplete>true</sendMessageOnCooldownComplete>
		<targetRequired>False</targetRequired>
